trans-unit.source: Represents the local print server (the computer on which your application is running) and enables management of its print queues.
trans-unit.target: 表示本地的打印服务器 （在其运行你的应用程序的计算机），并使其打印队列的管理。

trans-unit.source: When your application writes a value to a property of the LocalPrintServer object, that change has no effect until the value is passed to the computer that is represented by the LocalPrintServer object.
trans-unit.target: 当你的应用程序将一个值写入 LocalPrintServer 对象，该更改对象的属性不起作用之前的值传递给由 LocalPrintServer 对象表示的计算机。

trans-unit.source: To ensure that the change in value takes effect, use the <xref:System.Printing.LocalPrintServer.Commit%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保值更改生效，请使用<xref:System.Printing.LocalPrintServer.Commit%2A>方法。</xref:System.Printing.LocalPrintServer.Commit%2A>

trans-unit.source: In addition, other applications may also change the print service properties of the computer.
trans-unit.target: 此外，其他应用程序也可能更改的计算机的打印服务属性。

trans-unit.source: To ensure that the LocalPrintServer object used by your application has the latest actual values, use the <xref:System.Printing.LocalPrintServer.Refresh%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保使用你的应用程序的 LocalPrintServer 对象具有的最新的实际值，使用<xref:System.Printing.LocalPrintServer.Refresh%2A>方法。</xref:System.Printing.LocalPrintServer.Refresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!CAUTION]&1;> 类内<xref:System.Printing>命名空间不支持的 Windows 服务或 ASP.NET 应用程序或服务中的使用。</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: 尝试使用这些应用程序类型之一中的这些类可能会产生意外的问题，如降低服务性能和运行时异常。

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 如果你想要从 Windows 窗体应用程序打印，请参阅<xref:System.Drawing.Printing>命名空间。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>
